<area shape="rect" id="node6" title="dsgrid.dimension.dimension_filters.SupplementalDimensionFilterColumnOperatorModel

Filters base dimension records that have a valid mapping to a supplemental dimension.

Attributes:
 &#160;&#160;&#160;column (str): Column of dimension records to use. Default is &#39;id&#39;.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;value (Any): Value to filter on. Default is &#39;%&#39;.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;operator (str): Method on pyspark.sql.functions.col to invoke. Default is &#39;like&#39;.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;negate (bool): Filter out valid mappings to this supplemental dimension. Default is False.
" alt="" coords="4565,356,5411,376"/>
<area shape="rect" id="node7" title="dsgrid.query.models.DatasetModel

Specifies the datasets to use in a project query.

Attributes:
 &#160;&#160;&#160;dataset_id (str): Identifier for the resulting dataset
 &#160;&#160;&#160;source_datasets (List[Union[StandaloneDatasetModel, ProjectionDatasetModel]]): Datasets from which to read. Each must be of type DatasetBaseModel.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;expression (UnionType[str, NoneType]): Expression to combine datasets. Default is to take a union of all datasets. Default is None.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;params (ProjectQueryDatasetParamsModel): Parameters affecting datasets. Used for caching intermediate tables. Default is dimension_filters=[].
" alt="" coords="5,24,779,164"/>
<area shape="rect" id="node8" title="dsgrid.query.models.ProjectQueryDatasetParamsModel

Parameters in a project query that only apply to datasets

Attributes:
 &#160;&#160;&#160;dimension_filters (list[Annotated[Union[DimensionFilterExpressionModel, DimensionFilterExpressionRawModel, DimensionFilterColumnOperatorModel, DimensionFilterBetweenColumnOperatorModel, SubsetDimensionFilterModel, SupplementalDimensionFilterColumnOperatorModel], FieldInfo(annotation=NoneType, required=True, discriminator=&#39;filter_type&#39;)]]): Filters to apply to all datasets. Default is [].
" alt="" coords="923,154,4421,210"/>
<area shape="rect" id="node9" title="dsgrid.query.models.ProjectionDatasetModel

A dataset with growth rates that can be applied to a standalone dataset.

Attributes:
 &#160;&#160;&#160;dataset_id (str): Identifier for the resulting dataset
 &#160;&#160;&#160;initial_value_dataset_id (str): Principal dataset identifier
 &#160;&#160;&#160;growth_rate_dataset_id (str): Growth rate dataset identifier to apply to the principal dataset
 &#160;&#160;&#160;construction_method (DatasetConstructionMethod(str, Enum)): Specifier for the code that applies the growth rate to the principal dataset. Default is &#39;exponential_growth&#39;.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;base_year (Optional[int]): Base year of the dataset to use in growth rate application. Must be a year defined in the principal dataset&#39;s model year dimension. If None, there must be only one model year in that dimension and it will be used. Default is None.
" alt="" coords="2457,17,2887,37"/>
